  "tells": [
    "Hold Snuff Out until the opponent commits to a high-value spell to maximize the -1/-1 counter trigger",
    "Trigger Spellstutter Sprite on opponent's spells rather than your own to avoid self-inflicted counters",
    "Cast Lorien Revealed after the opponent has played multiple creatures to maximize life gain and board impact",
    "Common mistakes include overcommitting to Lorien Revealed without protection, misusing Spellstutter Sprite\u2019s sacrifice ability on low-impact spells, and failing to track opponent mana for sweepers.",
    "Unique interactions: Sprite\u2019s ability can be used to counter your own spells if needed, and Lorien Revealed tokens are flying and can be pumped."
